

how to download Unity:Please go to https://github.com/oppsmilo/2D-game/blob/main/pdf/How%20to%20download%20Unity.pdf



how to play this game:Please go to https://github.com/oppsmilo/2D-game/blob/main/%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88.zip
,click download and unzip the whole file.

if you enter game,click START GAME,


Keyboard manual:
UpArrow,LeftArrow,RightArrow:move
A:Basic attack
Z:Teleport right
X:Teleport right and top
Space:Release fire ball

if you want to leave:Please press Esc,you will quit the game immediately
